			<div class="alignright" ><a href="http://paxlupo.com/2013/04/11/covering-up-exxons-mayflower-mess/" rel="next">Covering Up Exxon&#8217;s Mayflower&nbsp;Mess &rarr;</a></div>
		</div><!--end pagination-->
